The sports day will begin soon.

85
00:04:09,660 --> 00:04:10,950
What should we do?

86
00:04:10,950 --> 00:04:11,790
Qin Ke'er.

87
00:04:11,830 --> 00:04:13,470
Will you stop behaving strangely?

88
