and figure it out.

106
00:05:18,590 --> 00:05:19,860
If you have time,

107
00:05:19,910 --> 00:05:21,550
please look for the dresses too.

108
00:05:21,790 --> 00:05:22,630
Thank you for the help.

109
00:05:24,550 --> 00:05:26,310
You're making things personal
against Tong Xi.

110
00:05:26,630 --> 00:05:27,070
You!

111
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:38,510
Dad, I lost the performance outfit.

112
00:05:38,550 --> 00:05:39,830
Can you please go to the town

113
00:05:39,830 --> 00:05:41,430
to see if you can find any plaid skirts?

114
00:05:51,390 --> 00:05:51,950
How is it going?

115
00:05:52,310 --> 00:05:53,350
I've looked around.

116
00:05:53,790 --> 00:05:55,030
I've even looked into rubbish bins

117
00:05:55,590 --> 00:05:56,630
but I couldn't find it.

118
00:05:57,070 --> 00:05:58,990
Why don't you 
go to the assembly point first?

119
00:05:59,190 --> 00:05:59,950
I'll look for it.

120
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:00,750
Let's go.

121
00:06:02,910 --> 00:06:03,990
Wait for me.

122
00:06:04,350 --> 00:06:06,300
Sir, something went missing in my class.

123
00:06:06,590 --> 00:06:09,030
Can I check the CCTV recordings?

124
00:06:10,470 --> 00:06:12,710
Ming, your class 
is going to perform Waltz, right?

125
00:06:12,750 --> 00:06:14,790
Why aren't you get changed yet?

126
00:06:15,070 --> 00:06:15,950
Enough, go away!

127
00:06:16,550 --> 00:06:18,310
My dad asked quite a few persons in town

128
00:06:18,910 --> 00:06:20,470
