suitable outfit for us.

129
00:06:21,630 --> 00:06:22,430
Sir.

130
00:06:22,830 --> 00:06:23,790
It's our turn?

131
00:06:23,790 --> 00:06:26,270
Where is the paint that we used

132
00:06:26,270 --> 00:06:26,830
for the posters?

133
00:06:27,150 --> 00:06:28,190
