134
00:06:31,670 --> 00:06:32,310
No.

135
00:06:34,470 --> 00:06:34,950
Here.

136
00:06:35,110 --> 00:06:36,190
You may paint your uniform...

137
00:06:36,190 --> 00:06:37,870
with your favourite colour and patterns.

138
00:06:38,030 --> 00:06:39,950
As for the ladies, you may

139
00:06:40,190 --> 00:06:41,830
tie your uniform around your waist.

140
00:06:42,430 --> 00:06:44,310
When you turn your body, 
it will look like a skirt.

141
00:06:44,670 --> 00:06:45,870
Here, choose the colour.

142
00:06:48,070 --> 00:06:48,590
Here.

