00:08:48,270 --> 00:08:50,230
[When I saw the smile on everyone's face,]

149
00:08:51,270 --> 00:08:52,310
[including Ni Xiao Wan's smile,]

150
00:08:52,830 --> 00:08:55,070
[I suddenly felt a gust 
of inexplicable happiness.]

151
00:08:56,630 --> 00:08:59,150
[The question is, 
do I really enjoy dancing?]

