00:09:59,350 --> 00:10:01,830
Wang Yi Ming won men's 100 meters.

158
00:10:06,580 --> 00:10:11,020
[The Sports Day's Post Mortem]

159
00:10:15,670 --> 00:10:16,590
Don't waste time.

160
