188
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:20,560
[The scripts of  "The Wizard of Oz"]

189
00:12:22,510 --> 00:12:23,110
Will you?

190
00:12:39,150 --> 00:12:39,830
Dad!

191
00:12:40,710 --> 00:12:41,590
Dad!

192
00:12:42,390 --> 00:12:43,030
You're here, Tong Tong.

193
00:12:43,030 --> 00:12:45,620
Happy birthday to you, dad.

194
00:12:45,620 --> 00:12:46,790
I'm no longer young.

195
00:12:46,790 --> 00:12:47,950
Why do you bring me cake?

196
00:12:49,190 --> 00:12:49,910
Let's dig in.

197
00:12:49,910 --> 00:12:51,150
I love cake the most.

198
00:12:53,750 --> 00:12:54,420
Where is your mum?

199
00:12:54,910 --> 00:12:55,950
Mum has to work over time.

200
00:12:55,950 --> 00:12:56,950
I guess she can't make it.

201
00:12:58,030 --> 00:12:59,550
All right, she's busy.

202
00:13:00,670 --> 00:13:01,550
No, I forgot that I'm cooking.

203
00:13:01,670 --> 00:13:02,870
Tong Tong, make yourself at home.

204
00:13:03,910 --> 00:13:05,350
Dad, be careful.

205
00:13:05,540 --> 00:13:06,350
I'm going up.

206
00:13:06,390 --> 00:13:06,910
Sure.

207
00:13:40,510 --> 00:13:41,870
Why do I see Lin Nan Yi everywhere?

208
00:13:44,380 --> 00:13:50,540
