210
00:13:48,750 --> 00:13:50,870
I'm going to Emerald City.

211
00:13:51,350 --> 00:13:53,030
Dear Oz...

212
00:13:57,070 --> 00:13:57,710
Are you rehearsing?

213
00:13:58,390 --> 00:13:59,460
Do you want to be an actress 
in the future?

214
00:14:00,910 --> 00:14:01,550
That's not right.

215
