218
00:14:10,710 --> 00:14:11,780
It's none of your business.

219
00:14:11,990 --> 00:14:13,910
My senior thinks that
I have the potential.

220
00:14:14,310 --> 00:14:15,870
He wants to train me. Is that wrong?

221
00:14:15,870 --> 00:14:16,990
Potential?

222
00:14:17,910 --> 00:14:20,110
Is the inability to recite the lines
considered as a type of potential too?

223
00:14:22,590 --> 00:14:24,230
Don't you dare to leave 
after being sarcastic to me.

224
00:14:24,540 --> 00:14:25,510
Rehearse the line with me.

225
00:14:26,150 --> 00:14:27,270
Me?

226
00:14:30,430 --> 00:14:31,670
I'm made of straws.

227
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:33,020
I don't have a brain.

228
00:14:34,510 --> 00:14:36,430
I feel so sorry for you.

229
00:14:37,590 --> 00:14:39,350
What do you think? If I

230
00:14:39,350 --> 00:14:40,990
go to Emerald City with you,

231
00:14:41,510 --> 00:14:44,110
will the Great Oz 
give me a pair of emerald...

232
00:14:45,270 --> 00:14:48,990
[There was the fragrance 
of soil and plants in the air.]

233
00:14:49,710 --> 00:14:52,470
[Nuan lived here alone.]

234
00:14:53,110 --> 00:14:56,190
[It's as if 
she had found her dream paradise.]

235
00:14:58,310 --> 00:15:00,630
[There was a pool of water 
in the middle of the garden.]

236
00:15:01,270 --> 00:15:03,150
[Nuan stood by the pool.]

237
00:15:03,630 --> 00:15:05,390
[The pool was muddy.]

238
00:15:05,990 --> 00:15:08,470
[A hoarse voice 
coming from the bottom of the pool asked,]

239
00:15:09,030 --> 00:15:10,510
["Why do you come here?"]

240
00:15:11,470 --> 00:15:14,310
Nuan answered, 
"I'm here to pursue my dream."

241
00:15:14,550 --> 00:15:16,510
"This place appeared in my dream."

242
00:15:16,670 --> 00:15:18,110
"I walked for a very long distance."

243
00:15:18,460 --> 00:15:20,310
"I've broken 800 pairs of shoes"

244
00:15:20,430 --> 00:15:21,750
"before I reached here."

245
00:15:23,270 --> 00:15:24,670
The hoarse voice laughed.

246
00:15:24,910 --> 00:15:26,950
He said, "I believe in you."

247
00:15:27,510 --> 00:15:29,830
"Dream is just like a beam of light."

248
00:15:30,230 --> 00:15:31,510
"When you're guided by your dream,"

249
00:15:31,780 --> 00:15:34,350
"you'll never lose your direction."

250
00:15:38,190 --> 00:15:38,710
By the way,

251
00:15:39,150 --> 00:15:39,990
I forgot to ask you.

252
00:15:40,140 --> 00:15:41,670
How's the opening performance?

253
00:15:41,950 --> 00:15:42,950
It went on smoothly.

254
00:15:43,110 --> 00:15:44,430
My class won an award.

255
00:15:45,030 --> 00:15:47,070
Have you discovered the charm of dancing?

256
00:15:50,990 --> 00:15:51,910
Not yet.

257
00:15:53,830 --> 00:15:54,910
I don't know how to put it.

258
00:15:55,670 --> 00:15:57,870
Since young, besides that performance,

259
00:15:58,110 --> 00:15:59,510
I only danced

260
00:15:59,510 --> 00:16:01,230
under my mom's request.

261
00:16:03,790 --> 00:16:05,780
Becoming a ballerina is her dream.

262
00:16:07,030 --> 00:16:08,070
It's not mine.

263
00:16:10,510 --> 00:16:11,470
What is your dream?

264
00:16:14,670 --> 00:16:15,790
I don't know yet.

265
00:16:21,470 --> 00:16:23,790
Tong Tong, it's time to eat.

266
00:16:24,590 --> 00:16:25,110
I'm coming.

267
00:16:29,390 --> 00:16:30,190
Let's dig in.

268
00:16:30,950 --> 00:16:31,670
Let me taste the meat.

269
00:16:33,180 --> 00:16:33,790
How is it?

270
00:16:35,870 --> 00:16:37,310
The taste is way better than the look.

271
00:16:37,550 --> 00:16:39,390
Dad, you've improved.

272
00:16:39,430 --> 00:16:40,310
You should eat more.

273
00:16:45,350 --> 00:16:45,910
I'm hungry.

274
00:16:46,670 --> 00:16:47,700
I want to go home and eat.

275
00:16:49,150 --> 00:16:50,270
